### ============================================================
### 찜 (Wishlist) — 미구현
### ============================================================

### POST /wishlists — 찜 등록

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/wishlists
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: BUYER

{
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099"
}

###

### DELETE /wishlists/{wishlistId} — 찜 삭제

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/wishlists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: BUYER

###

### GET /wishlists — 찜한 상품 목록

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/wishlists?page=0&size=20
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: BUYER

###

### GET /wishlists/exists — 찜 여부 확인

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/wishlists/exists?productId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
X-User-Role: BUYER

###

### ============================================================
### 관리자 — 사용자 관리
### X-User-Id에 {{adminUserId}} 사용
### ============================================================

### GET /admin/users — 전체 조회 (필터 없음)

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### GET /admin/users — status=active 필터

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users?status=active
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### GET /admin/users — status=suspended 필터

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users?status=suspended
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### GET /admin/users — role=buyer 필터

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users?role=buyer
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### GET /admin/users — keyword 검색

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users?keyword=관리자
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### GET /admin/users — 페이지네이션

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users?page=1&size=5
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### GET /admin/users — 유효하지 않은 status (에러: 400 예상)

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users?status=INVALID
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### GET /admin/stats/users — 회원 통계 조회

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/stats/users
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### PATCH /admin/users/{userId}/status — 사용자 상태 변경

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/{{userId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

{
  "status": "active"
}

###

### ============================================================
### 관리자 — 판매자 심사
### ============================================================

### GET /admin/sellers/register — 판매자 신청 목록

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/sellers/register?page=1&size=20&status=ALL
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### PATCH /admin/sellers/register/{registerId}/approve — 승인

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/sellers/register/a5e01f76-9764-4c53-8571-c843177614db/approve
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### PATCH /admin/sellers/register/{registerId}/reject — 반려

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/sellers/register/16588492-69f7-481a-85ff-7ce00cec1200/reject
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: ADMIN

{
  "rejectReason": "포트폴리오가 확인되지 않습니다. 샘플을 보완 후 재신청해 주세요."
}

